    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Just browserify your tests directly. The \"production like\" vs testing all in one bundle would be testing browserify and your minifier instead of testing your application code. It's best and simplest to just browserify your test files directly. There will be some factoring logic with [factor-bundle](https://npmjs.org/package/factor-bundle) landing in plugin-space soon but factored bundles are for the use-case of minimizing multi-page payloads.\n",
